```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant PC as Windows Host
    participant AD as A_device (TinyUSB)
    participant BH as B_host (TinyUSB Host)
    participant HID as Real HID Device

    HID->>BH: tuhhid_mount_cb (descriptor streams)
    BH-->>AD: PF_DESC_REPORT / DEVICE / CONFIG chunks
    BH-->>AD: PF_DESC_DONE
    BH-->>AD: PF_CTRL_DEVICE_RESET
    AD->>AD: tinyusb_restart()
    AD->>PC: TinyUSB connect, enumeration begins
    PC->>AD: GET_DESCRIPTOR (Strings 0..2)
    AD->>BH: PF_CTRL_STRING_REQ
    BH->>HID: tuh_descriptor_get_string (optional)
    BH-->>AD: PF_DESC_STRING / fallback
    AD-->>PC: String descriptor (or STALL for idx>2)
    AD->>PC: READY control frame (after tud_mount_cb)
    PC->>AD: SET_IDLE / GET_REPORT etc.
    AD->>BH: PF_CTRL_SET_IDLE / GET_REPORT
    BH->>HID: Forward control transfer
    BH-->>AD: PF_CTRL_GET_REPORT response / SET_IDLE ack
    AD-->>PC: HID report data stream (tud_hid_report)
    HID-->>BH: tuh_hid_report_callback (input data)
    BH-->>AD: PF_INPUT frames

    Note over AD,BH: PF_UNMOUNT triggers remote_desc_reset() & TinyUSB shutdown
```
